{"about_the_game":"The invasion has been raging for hundreds of years and the Courines are starting to flee their own lands. A plague of strange creatures controlled by an enemy faction are infecting the land and Greak must reunite with his older brother (Raydel) and his sister (Adara) to escape. The only way to survive is by using their unique abilities between them to navigate the dangers ahead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hand-Drawn Art and Animation:</h2>Enjoy a captivating story line about family, home and union in difficult times while you discover colorful and expressive scenarios.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/extras/Greak_Steam_Art.gif?t=1726586084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Specially Crafted Puzzles:</h2>Solve specially crafted puzzles to find and collect the missing pieces of an Airship through an Interconnected World<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/extras/Greak_Steam_Puzzles.gif?t=1726586084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Gameplay:</h2>Alternate between the three characters and use their different abilities to explore the Magical lands of Azur.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/extras/Greak_Steam_GamePlay.gif?t=1726586084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fast-Paced Combat: </h2>Discover new areas and fight against a wide variety of enemies to rescue the Courines from the Urlag invasion.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/extras/Greak_Steam_Combat.gif?t=1726586084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cinematic Clips: </h2>Throughout the game, you will encounter beautiful hand-drawn cinematic clips that will accompany key story moments to immerse you into the world of Azur.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/extras/Greak_Steam_CinemClips.gif?t=1726586084\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Live Orchestra Soundtrack:</h2>Enjoy the expressive and atmospheric music themes specially created to experience a unique adventure.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Adventure Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/9ccf68c210be4a06ceada4b08095990718a648af.jpg"},{"name":"Courine's Recipe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/cfbfe2273e4c5d7852682d6080c1bf2c239ad5c3.jpg"},{"name":"An Escape Plan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/854e718564d0bb490a0941e9af50b638f21de979.jpg"},{"name":"I Missed Your Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/525293143e466e3cc8a0a20f765bbf784dd9c0b5.jpg"},{"name":"A Family Reunion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/3be5e369a7e921ec501217cbb3fca477a9fe826b.jpg"},{"name":"A View of Azur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/677e5bba8bb12734978454692adea2b898062ea7.jpg"},{"name":"More Than You Need","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/a0b708782142812c2bad50ec4eedcefe43ac7a43.jpg"},{"name":"Forest Restorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/3294010e90646a83845796c7703f2b43eccc06c4.jpg"},{"name":"Scout\u00b4s Training","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/312bb3011faed08830639b56218befe2230bd509.jpg"},{"name":"Fearless Courine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1311070/b8a9d6b3fcf25a6346fd5e5d01f211241593c235.jpg"}],"total":24},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311070/page